# Gemini API keys for llm_evaluate.py — one key per line.
#
# Copy this file to `secrets/gemini_keys.txt` and add your keys. The
# `.txt` file is gitignored; this `.example` is committed as a template.
#
# Get keys at: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# Free tier: ~15 RPM per key for gemini-2.5-flash-lite. Add multiple keys
# from different Google accounts to multiply throughput.
#
# Lines starting with `#` and blank lines are ignored.
# Whitespace around keys is trimmed.

# AIzaSy...your-first-key...
# AIzaSy...second-key...
# AIzaSy...third-key...
